{"tid":531583,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母狗巴個Apps真係冇撚用","createTime":"2018-01-17T03:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T17:38:22.000Z","uid":66280,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3ec82346d9cca9448fb339b8e566624de0ce9efa","tid":531583,"uid":66280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"痴撚線都出唔到個時間<br />\n每次行落去都同個Apps講個時間唔撚一樣<br />\n然後個Apps又出唔到個時間出嚟<br />\n咁佢整個Apps出嚟把撚啦<br />\n屌佢老母又加價<br />\n整出嚟啲野又廢<br />\n執柒咗佢啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"ad5318d9b0efea1de5f1aa320dc8e9fe30bec87d","tid":531583,"uid":54927,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:52:23.000Z","msg":"次次都準喎"},{"pid":"87ea5509c214e68a84c515001364191b1774659a","tid":531583,"uid":142629,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"講到咁把炮就唔好再搭巴士啦<br />\n搭的士算啦"},{"pid":"e69be3f38567612f25403f2833545ef09984d324","tid":531583,"uid":130901,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:54:36.000Z","msg":"準喎<br />\n不過搵路線方面好廢"},{"pid":"ca0da4a940e08d6c20230d75751d80f102180d83","tid":531583,"uid":34023,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"上面做乜野<br />\n你整個app出黎就有責任搞好佢嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講番個app<br />\n繁忙時間佢係唔多準<br />\n有時個時間仲會轉黎轉去<br />\n好多人仲投訴個時間顯示唔到，會變左空白<br />\n所以唔好依賴晒佢"},{"pid":"e0ef468f10e405fa4961b2a579976cb7b9a2164f","tid":531583,"uid":67009,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"好過城巴 乜柒都冇"},{"pid":"d6d37e21c04e21a04e526a7f6ec1e161c6641c8f","tid":531583,"uid":41737,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T04:04:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f13002c2d780b4a31d4cccc0aba6228ddfdff669","tid":531583,"uid":34023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上面做乜野<br />\n你整個app出黎就有責任搞好佢嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講番個app<br />\n繁忙時間佢係唔多準<br />\n有時個時間仲會轉黎轉去<br />\n好多人仲投訴個時間顯示唔到，會變左空白<br />\n所以唔好依賴晒佢</blockquote>以前冇app咪又係咁搭<br />\n整左出黎 冇十成準 得九成準<br />\n都要畀人屌到反艇<br />\n唔鍾意咪唔好睇 學以前咁鳩等囉<br />\n香港人真係難服侍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱呀<br />\n非繁忙時間其實好有用<br />\n有時我揀坐咩交通工具果陣<br />\n可以睇定先，見到唔夠時間行去車站我就會坐其他，方便左好多"},{"pid":"0136a298a9518e6d8f8e5854b0866866a717c812","tid":531583,"uid":36478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e926f4e13dbf9c43eb67075953c8f1c71d398381","tid":531583,"uid":154901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T10:26:07.000Z","msg":"個到站時間係受到路況影響既, 有時Show出黎咪預多少少走盞, 唔係下下要100%準確先叫有用APP掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b314780c7b7584f4410f8393dd944af636ab7d40","tid":531583,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:18:21.000Z","msg":"不過真係成日都出唔到個時間"},{"pid":"67cc3b2dba72d58a0b1a36154b5369515dadfc26","tid":531583,"uid":34023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過真係成日都出唔到個時間</blockquote><br />\n同埋我發覺佢一開app彈出黎個廣告<br />\n你禁X, 十次有九次會中左個廣告開browser"},{"pid":"fe89f23f47dfa60c42022be0776d30e14590a18c","tid":531583,"uid":46332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"67cc3b2dba72d58a0b1a36154b5369515dadfc26","tid":531583,"uid":34023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過真係成日都出唔到個時間</blockquote><br />\n同埋我發覺佢一開app彈出黎個廣告<br />\n你禁X, 十次有九次會中左個廣告開browser"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:09:42.000Z","msg":"好撚討厭<br />\napp入面有banner都或者可以接受<br />\n最好咪撚有<br />\n大佬趕住搵/睇你仲彈個全page出黎要我撳X 仲要冒住會彈去網頁嘅風險浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e3906f0840c44ca0800a115af2652fcaa3cb0d","tid":531583,"uid":1274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:31:53.000Z","msg":"有一次apps明明顯示仲有一分鐘有車到，點知就冇車來，app又明顯30分鐘後有車到，咁唯有繼續等，等多半個鍾，點知都係無車，app又跳出去顯示30分鐘後有車到，我屌佢老母冚家鏟啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d3b4303f057b5dc0ce1bf816af2378e1a7bddf","tid":531583,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"聯營線真係亂到七彩<br />\n搭118冇一次係準嘅<br />\n明明個app話仲有7分鐘先到站<br />\n但架巴士已經到咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c004772e917fca421b10b2b24e9fe43177b3dc41","tid":531583,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0ef468f10e405fa4961b2a579976cb7b9a2164f","tid":531583,"uid":67009,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"好過城巴 乜柒都冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:35:27.000Z","msg":"成堆賺錢線加咗ETA啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9db1e758399ecaeb84756b94b1a436e56816baf","tid":531583,"uid":21407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58d3b4303f057b5dc0ce1bf816af2378e1a7bddf","tid":531583,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"聯營線真係亂到七彩<br />\n搭118冇一次係準嘅<br />\n明明個app話仲有7分鐘先到站<br />\n但架巴士已經到咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:37:44.000Z","msg":"以前我做嘅時候 係set死左咩時間會係城巴slot<br />\n不過曾經試過如果九巴一脫班 就會出城巴時段班次<img src=\"/assets/f